Pre-Game Insights: Bafana Bafana and Morocco meet in the Round of 16 at the Africa Cup of Nations tournament in Ivory Coast.
South Africa qualified after finishing in second place in Group, behind leaders Mali.
Morocco topped group F after picking up two victories and a draw.
Others: The match between Bafana and Morocco will be televised live on SuperSport PSL as well as SABC1.
The two sides meet on Tuesday 30 January 2024! Action is scheduled to get underway at 22:00 SAST.
